// =====================================================================
// Vibe Coding block: Homepage · Before / After Brieflee
// =====================================================================
// Sits below the hero on the homepage. Foreplay-style two-card section.
//
// Design rules locked in this block (apply to ALL future marketing
// blocks unless explicitly overridden):
//   - Section heading h2: text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold
//     tracking-tight leading-[1.1] (matches lead-magnet faq.jsx)
//   - font-weight 700 max for body sections. NEVER 800 outside the hero.
//   - Eyebrow: copy of the hero's Eyebrow component (peri-tinted pill,
//     14px, navy text, 8px dot with peri ring) — verbatim.
//   - Section background: HERO_BG (cloud-in-the-middle radial gradient,
